      • TileInfo_Impl

        public TileInfo_Impl(java.lang.String name,
                     java.awt.Image image,
                     java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object> fields)
        Constructor, takes all data required about the tile. An exception will be thrown if the data provided is invalid.
        Parameters:
        name - -name/type of the tile (e.g 'Free', 'ExitDoor', etc)
        image - -the image for the tile
        fields - -a map of any other fields in the tile object. -the key = the name of the field as a string and the value = the value of the fields -e.g for LockedDoor this will contain: key='id', value=id(int)
